Template: task-teacats/config
Type: multiselect
Choices: Hostname, Network, SSH, Postfix, NTP
Default: Hostname, Network, SSH, Postfix, NTP
Description: Select Package to Configure
 Select which other packages task-teacats should automatically
 configure for you.

Template: task-teacats/hostname
Type: string
Default: ${default}
Description: Machine Hostname
 Fully-Qualified Hostname of the machine

Template: task-teacats/interface
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Default: ${default}
Description: Network Interface
 Name of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/address-ipv4
Type: string
Default:
Description: Network Interface IPv4 Address
 Address of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/netmask-ipv4
Type: string
Default: 24
Description: Network Interface IPv4 Network Mask
 Network mark of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/gateway-ipv4
Type: string
Description: Network Interface IPv4 Default Gateway
 Default Gateway of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/address-local
Type: string
Default: 192.168.0.0
Description: Network Interface Local Address
 Address of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/netmask-local
Type: string
Default: 17
Description: Network Interface Local Network Mask
 Network mark of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/address-ipv6
Type: string
Default:
Description: Network Interface IPv6 Address
 Address of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/netmask-ipv6
Type: string
Default: 64
Description: Network Interface IPv6 Network Mask
 Network mark of the network interface

Template: task-teacats/gateway-ipv6
Type: string
Default: fe80::1
Description: Network Interface IPv6 Default Gateway
 Default Gateway of the network interface
